Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.07,0:00:05.77,Header,,0,0,0,,This is a Gentlemen of the Hàn free fansub.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:06.42,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,250.286)\fade(255,0,255,0,1820,4700,5900)}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:06.42,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346.276,408)\fade(255,0,255,0,1820,4700,5900)}Dǒng Zhuó takes control of the capital
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the current Emperor is weak and incapable,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Prince of Chénliú is\Nsmart and studious, like a true monarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, before the army, \NHis Grace displayed his authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a commanding presence\Nis rare in a boy his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,if I were to depose the emperor and enthrone the Prince of Chénliú,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,would this be feasible?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:40.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(598,368)\fade(255,0,255,0,320,2100,2460)}Dǒng Zhuó\NStyled: Zhòngyǐng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:47.14,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(88.715,361.143)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,2420,2820)}Lǐ Rú
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If your lordship wishes to gain authority\N by deposing the emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,then it is a splendid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}I've long garrisoned at Xīliáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}These problems in the court...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}How can I establish my authority in just a few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}I believe the answer is to depose the emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}and crown a new sovereign!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Depose the old and crown the new.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By deposing the Emperor, \Nyou will earn two boons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.87,0:01:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}Of old, both Yī Yǐn and Huò Guāng deposed their ruler to enthrone a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:37.70,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Yī Yǐn was a chancellor who helped the founding of the Shang dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:42.70,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Huo Guang was a general, later minister of Han dynasty who helped stabilize the government following Emperor Wu's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}They became respected, outstanding figures of their era.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}If you, my lord, follow their example,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}You are sure to go down in history.\NThis is the first boon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the second?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}For the great deed of saving the Emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}you can use it to lord over all ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}With this, who would dare to oppose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}When the new monarch is enthroned,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}your lordship can overrule the Son of Heaven to command the ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}Thus, you can take over the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,432.286)}This is the second boon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly give wit to these old bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With these two boon, why not act now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there are boons, there is still one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}Ever since the two Emperors \NZhāng and Hé ascended to the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}those who held the authority within the imperial court,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}such as Dòu Xiàn, Dèng Zhì, Yán Xiǎn, Chén Fān,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}and until recently, Generalissimo Hé Jìn, murdered by the Ten Attendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}there is not one who didn't suffer a violent death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}I ask of you, my lord, to forgive my blunt words,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}but the one who controls the emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}will undoubtedly be the real authority at the court,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}but will also make himself a target to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}I hope my lord would take this one trouble into consideration and acts cautiously!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}Knowing the past, understanding the present!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.328,428.286)}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.008,420.667)}Your words are honest, \Nvery good. Very true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.008,420.667)}However, I, Dǒng Zhuó,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.008,420.667)}am not Dòu Xiàn, Dèng Zhì, or those others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.008,420.667)}And I am definitely not that lowly butcher, Hé Jìn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.008,420.667)}Since there are two boons but only one problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.008,420.667)}what's there to fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.65,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(93.294,361.143)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,20420,28020)}Bào Xìn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.50,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(119,366.857)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,24290,28920)}Yuán Shào\NStyled: Běnchū
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}The nation is in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}the spirits are in turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:52.37,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: The spirits mentioned are the spirits of grain and soil, which received regular sacrifices during the Hàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}Though the Ten Attendants were eliminated,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}now Dǒng Zhuó has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}Every day, he goes to the districts running amok,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}with his elite soldiers to clear the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}The commoners hide from him as if he were a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}He's causing panic in and around the capital city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}Had we known then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}we wouldn't have involved him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}Now he goes in and out the palace as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}He is unscrupulous, all the officials fear him, and the Emperor feels no peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}Before, Zhèng Tài and Lú Zhí had warned that \NDǒng Zhuó may look kind, but is cruel as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}that once he entered\N the palace, disaster would follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}Their concerns proved to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}I sense Dǒng Zhuó harbors grand ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}Eliminate him as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}What do you two think? Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}Colonel Bào, how can't I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}But the chaos caused by \Nthe Ten Attendants has only just subsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.321,426)}This court has only recently established,\N it's too soon to act rashly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Minister over the Masses{\i0},\Nwhat do you propose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.14,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(101,356)}Wáng Yǔn\NStyled: Zǐshī
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We may discuss this issue again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, I shall lead my army out of the capital for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're ready to fight Dǒng Zhuó, I shall return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, Lord Dǒng sends this invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, Dǒng Zhuó invites all the officials to Wēn Garden for a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.02,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600.878,369.143)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,1380,1780)}Dīng Yuán\NStyled: Jiànyáng
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.94,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(581,362.286)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,1580,1980)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.77,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(571.18,364.571)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,2420,2820)}Lǚ Bù\NStyled: Fèngxiān
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Běnchū.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have arrived late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit, sit, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have come from Xīliáng to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Recently, I wanted to consult with you all on one or two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I have prepared some light wine.\NWould you fellows drink some?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Merely the presence being with you all makes me feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng, after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you gentlemen not to be alarmed. I have something to say, so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}Ever since ancient times, the Emperor served as the overlord for thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}Exalted by all, and must never fail\Nto pay his respects at the ancestral temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}and uphold the national spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}And now? His Majesty is \Ncowardly, weak, and uncouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}He is inferior to the Prince of Chénliú, who is intelligent and astute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}I propose we depose the young emperor\Nand replace him with the Prince of Chénliú.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}Otherwise, if you fellows have no objections-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}Who do you think you are?\N Daring to speak blasphemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}The Emperor is his late majesty's legitimate son!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}He has made no transgression,\Nhow could we depose him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}This is akin to usurping the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}From this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}those who obey me prosper,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}those that don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}Today is for feasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}Let's not talk about politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.855,434.571)}No more politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiànyáng, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiànyáng, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiànyáng, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó, you traitor!\NYou won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were my honest words! Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the Ten Attendants may be gone\Nbut the new regime has only been established!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds of issues need addressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation is unstable.\Nthis will only cause problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I considered it! This is what's \Nbest for the nation's spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Běnchū, what do you have to fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, this is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:04.46,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(102.519,348.571)}Lú Zhí\NStyled: Zǐgàn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}Of old, during Tài Jiǎ's reign,\NYī Yǐn imprisoned him at Tóng Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}When the Prince of Chāngyì was enthroned, merely 27 days after,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}his crimes numbered over 3,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}and thus Huò Guāng deposed him in the ancestral temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}Today, the Emperor, while young, is still wise and keen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}He has not committed the slightest of crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}You, sir, are only an overseer of a frontier region, not adept in state affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}You also lack the talent of Yī Yǐn and Huò Guāng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)}How could you talk about an\Nimportant matter like deposition so lightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.408,428.857)}Sages have said, "Allowed are those of Yī Yǐn's will,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.408,428.857)} "usurpers are those lost of Yī Yǐn's will!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you first, villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.14,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,360)}Lú Zhí\NStyled: Zǐgàn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng, Director Lú is respected by people the world over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing him would appall all in the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the scare!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the proposal by Lord Dǒng to depose the emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is of a foremost matter to the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Respectfully, it is improper to discuss it after drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's discuss it at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng, your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wáng Yǔn takes his leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We take our leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The nation is unfortunate for the eunuchs to\Nseize power, and now you abuse the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you Dīng Yuán!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had Lǚ Bù,\Nnothing in the world could worry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù and I are from the same village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know him very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very brave, but not bright\Nand would sell his soul to the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am willing to use my silver tongue\Nto convince Lǚ Bù to turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can convince Lǚ Bù?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven is on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you win him over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hear, my lord, has a famous steed by the name of Red Hare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to persuade Lǚ Bù, I need that horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't convince him without the horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}Lǚ Bù is a valiant warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}Among the things that a warrior loves,\Nthe first is a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}Second is a horse, and the third is armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}These are the three things \Nthat a warrior needs to excel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}Today, what Lǚ Bù rode is\Nmerely an ordinary warhorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}How can he not crave for a fine steed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}Red Hare, a precious horse,\Nas far as Your Lordship is concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}is nothing but a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}But for fighting on the battlefield,\Nespecially for a renowned general,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}it's as important as his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}Lǚ Bù already possesses the Sky Piercing halberd
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}and on his body, he wears a fine suit of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}All of these are no ordinary things.\NHe only lacks a good steed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}If he obtains Red Hare, it would\N be like giving a tiger wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}My lord, if you want Lǚ Bù on your side,\Nhere is what I suggest:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}Any other horse is not enough to sway his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}and not enough to show Your Lordship's sincerity because,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}my lord, can you really give up this horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}If he gets the horse, add some precious jewels to help sway his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}I can persuade him by explaining the advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}I am sure that Lǚ Bù will betray Dīng Yuán\Nand come to your side, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}My lord, if you want to seize the realm,\Nwhy care about a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.90,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(105.886,206.857)}Lǐ Sù
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348.566,422)}Very well, I shall give up my horse!
