Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sù,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't expect you'd come visit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, bring food and wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, Brother Sù, for gifting me such a fine steed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly don't know how to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A precious sword belongs to a warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a precious horse belongs to a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you're a tiger of the world, Red Hare is a dragon among horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This horse could only belong to you, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Time does flies. Brother Sù, what are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}General of the Gentlemen of the Household{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how far you've gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, are you content?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now I serve under Overseer Dīng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, I hardly see you anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but I do often see your esteemed father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you must be drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My father has been dead for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you meet him, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I am talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Overseer Dīng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Very witty, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.15,0:22:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not saying this to flatter you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but with your talents...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you wasting them under Overseer Dīng?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:22:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Light the torches!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Light the torches!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.84,0:23:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you possess the talent to\Nhold the sky and sail the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone within the four seas\Nthat doesn't admire you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Achieving wealth and prestige for you is as easy as taking from a pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have no choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, don't you know this story,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that a good bird chooses a good tree to perch,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a good minister chooses a worthy lord to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, there are more people and heroes\Nin the world that have extraordinary talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, if you continue to follow Dīng Jiànyáng,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you build a meritorious career?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.95,0:24:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to find a worthy lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish brother, I've come here\N precisely for your future career.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, who do you think is the hero of our era?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, there is no harm in speaking your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.17,0:24:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.47,0:24:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.20,0:24:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.69,0:24:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Having observed the vast realm, among all the\Nministers, I consider them all inferior to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.84,0:24:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.85,0:24:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.76,0:24:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.80,0:24:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.59,0:24:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, even a hero such as yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.06,0:25:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon he hears Dǒng Zhuó's name,\Nchanges the color of his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.97,0:25:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó truly is a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.68,0:25:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you really know how to joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.50,0:25:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can that traitor be a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.48,0:25:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó is tyrannical and eyes of usurpation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.91,0:25:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How could everyone within the court not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.91,0:25:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But you-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.86,0:25:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.25,0:25:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you only know his image,\Nand not his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.31,0:25:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You only know one aspect,\Nand not the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.53,0:25:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emperor is weak,\N unable to control the ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.88,0:25:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How could all the officials at court not know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.36,0:25:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince of Chénliú is\Nintelligent, strong, and astute,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.17,0:25:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,apter than the Emperor a hundred fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.92,0:25:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, how could all the officials at court not know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.90,0:25:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have these thoughts,\Nbut nobody says it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.84,0:25:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.11,0:25:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They fear leaving a reputation of disloyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.62,0:25:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and being labeled as criminals,\Nexploiting the chaos to usurp the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.77,0:26:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A weak Son of Heaven is easy to fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.53,0:26:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but a strong Son of Heaven is hard to fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.44,0:26:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The court officials are loyal on the outside,\Nbut deep down they think of their own benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.59,0:26:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think truly serves\Nthe empire and nation's spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.89,0:26:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng is not like them,\Nhe dares to say what others dare not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.11,0:26:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He speaks words others would not say out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.28,0:26:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He dares the risk of leaving a negative reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.48,0:26:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He bears the accusations of usurpation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.41,0:26:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart of Lord Dǒng is pure,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the actions of Lord Dǒng are righteous!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.50,0:26:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I 've never heard such words before,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.93,0:26:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't seem unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.71,0:26:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.24,0:26:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to depose the Emperor\Nis the road to usurpation!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.02,0:26:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.94,0:26:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Since ancient times, only the virtuous were able to hold paramount authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.61,0:27:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Presently, the Prince and Emperor\Nare both sons of the late emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.60,0:27:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If he assists the Prince in taking the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.25,0:27:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how is that usurpation? This is my first point.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.86,0:27:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The second:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.97,0:27:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When the late emperor was still reigning,\Nhe favored the Prince of Chénliú,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.02,0:27:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that he intended to have him succeed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.68,0:27:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Empress Hé and Hé Jìn who forced a change in heir, a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.57,0:27:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng will now depose the Emperor\Nand enthrone the Prince of Chénliú
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.46,0:27:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in accordance with the late emperor's original will,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.02,0:27:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,restoring the throne to the Prince of Chénliú.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.48,0:27:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that treacherous?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.77,0:27:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother, hearing your words is like\nclouds parting to for the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.94,0:27:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have enlightened me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.97,0:27:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, there are 10,000 reasons why you shouldn't\Nhesitate and miss such an opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.95,0:28:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone as insignificant as me under Lord Dǒng
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.46,0:28:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,can become {\i1}General of the Gentlemen of the Household,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.62,0:28:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then you, with your great courage and talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.33,0:28:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,are sure to have a meteoric\Nrise under Lord Dǒng.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.78,0:28:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You would quickly climb up the ranks and be rewarded beyond what you could imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.80,0:28:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.13,0:28:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.26,0:28:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no way to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.46,0:28:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.84,0:28:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,please look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.06,0:28:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.73,0:28:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng has long admired your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.97,0:28:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He intends to make a friend of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.62,0:28:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng ordered me to give you\Nthese gifts to pay his respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.19,0:28:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That precious horse, Red Hare,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.63,0:28:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,was Lord Dǒng's favorite mount.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.09,0:28:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng sends it as a special gift to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.95,0:29:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.51,0:29:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,shows me such kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.17,0:29:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, Lord Dǒng has been thinking of your great name for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.48,0:29:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Dǒng has shown me so much favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.86,0:29:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but I regret that I, Lǚ Bù,\Nhave done nothing in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.95,0:29:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no gift to offer when I meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.01,0:29:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, the merits you seek are here and it is as easy as turning your hand over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.81,0:29:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whom does Lord Dǒng want to eliminate?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.41,0:29:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.82,0:30:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I only fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.94,0:30:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be willing to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.86,0:30:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.91,0:30:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I, a real man, ever be your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.43,0:30:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān! Why are you saying this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.01,0:31:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Obtaining you, General, is like a seedling tasting sweet-dew in a drought!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.42,0:31:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.08,0:31:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.49,0:31:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.56,0:31:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.48,0:31:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have wandered half my life. My only regret was not having met such a worthy lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.71,0:31:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, if you would allow,\NI, Bù, would treat you as his own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.93,0:31:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Fèngxiān is by my side! Heaven has blessed me with such an outstanding hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.71,0:31:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.86,0:31:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.38,0:32:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, from now on, your son will follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.51,0:32:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Through water and fire, I will never give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.82,0:32:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I aid you to achieve this grand undertaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.16,0:32:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With Fèngxiān with me,\NI can accomplish my ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.44,0:32:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.67,0:32:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.95,0:32:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby name you {\i1}Chief Cavalry Commander to the Gentlemen of the Household{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.82,0:32:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with the noble rank of Marquis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.50,0:32:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.74,0:32:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Present golden armor\Nand silk brocade robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.90,0:32:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, your father will summon the officials
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.73,0:32:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to re-discuss deposing the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.53,0:32:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son is willing to escort you, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.79,0:32:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you to bring 1,000 armed men\N to be your father's bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.42,0:32:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.55,0:32:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.35,0:32:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the current emperor is ignorant,\Nunworthy to his forefathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.32,0:32:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall follow the examples of Yī Yǐn and Huò Guāng.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.44,0:33:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The emperor hereafter shall be \Nknown as the Prince of Hóngnóng,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.13,0:33:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the Prince of Chénliú will be the new sovereign.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.63,0:33:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who disobey will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.68,0:33:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.08,0:33:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the regime is still new,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.46,0:33:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you were summoned to assist\Nthe Emperor to restore order!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.68,0:33:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.13,0:33:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,have repeatedly called meetings to\Ndepose an imperial firstborn son!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.33,0:33:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to rebel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.20,0:33:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The realm's affairs rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.93,0:34:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is my command,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.57,0:34:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd dare to oppose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.25,0:34:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The realm relies on the Emperor and the loyal ministers here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.00,0:34:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.55,0:34:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,are merely just a traitor and a usurper!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.66,0:34:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should you matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.28,0:34:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to see if my sword is sharp enough, whelp?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.98,0:34:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine isn't dull either!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.57,0:34:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's been settled yet! No need for strife!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.13,0:34:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Běnchū!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.28,0:34:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Běnchū...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.08,0:35:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,On the ninth month on the first day, we shall hold a ceremony of deposition and ascension at Jiādé Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.88,0:35:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All the civil and military officials must be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.02,0:35:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.57,0:35:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuán Shào!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.12,0:35:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuán Shào!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.12,0:35:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an useless official you are, unworthy of the empire's favor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.03,0:36:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuó, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.54,0:36:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you to assassinate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.54,0:36:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare conspire against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.34,0:36:39.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(123,352)}Wǔ Fú\NStyled: Déyú
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.12,0:36:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.868,427.714)}You are not my monarch, I am not your subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.86,0:36:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.868,427.714)}What is there to 'conspire'?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.98,0:36:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.868,427.714)}Your crimes fill the very Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.52,0:36:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.868,427.714)}Everyone wants to see you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.80,0:36:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.868,427.714)}I only regret not cutting you to \Npieces as to appease the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.72,0:37:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.00,0:37:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! Vile traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.08,0:37:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You will go down in history as a byword of infamy for 10,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.50,0:37:33.66,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(144.807,315.429)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,20420,28200)}Emperor Shǎo of Hàn
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.40,0:37:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}Emperor Xiàolíng left his subjects all too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.80,0:37:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}The Emperor succeeded him as the heir and everyone within the four seas looked up at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.97,0:37:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}However the Emperor is frivolous, inmajestic, and insolemn.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.02,0:38:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}In the mourning of his predecessor, his father, he proved to be slow and indolent.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.57,0:38:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}He is an embarrassment to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.54,0:38:07.78,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(128.78,250.286)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,1820,2220)}Empress Dowager Hé
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.92,0:38:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}The Empress Dowager didn't teach her son\Nproperly as a mother should,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.70,0:38:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}consequently the affairs of the realm are in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.15,0:38:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}Empress Yǒnglè died suddenly,\Nwhich aroused public suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.77,0:38:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}Isn't evident that the rules of the three essentials:\NHeaven, Earth, and Human, have been violated?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.22,0:38:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}The Prince of Chénliú is dutiful, divinely virtuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.44,0:38:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}and solemnly observes proper etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.82,0:38:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}During the national mourning, he was sorrowful and has never said anything improper.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.65,0:38:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}The entire realm has heard of his excellent behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.35,0:38:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}He is therefore suitable to rule the vast empire and unify it for the next 10,000 generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.17,0:38:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}We hereby depose the Emperor,\Ndemoting him to the Prince of Hóngnóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.46,0:38:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.711,446)}The Empress Dowager\N shall relinquish all her authority.
